{"tid":2282362,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–基因編輯技術的最新進展Prime Editing","createTime":"2020-11-11T22:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T18:07:16.000Z","uid":38861,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4b3d30445c493d5fd0909634672292d8dd610532","tid":2282362,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T22:56:53.000Z","msg":"現今已知接近有7萬幾種的基因變異會引起疾病。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N6CYb7T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN6CYb7T.png&h=0fbd2e8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著CRISPR基因編輯技術的興起，將會為根治這些疾病帶來曙光。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）圖中將展示「舊式」的編輯方法HDR（Homology Directed Repair)機制。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U6DAemh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU6DAemh.jpg&h=ecc57bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsgRNA將會引領Cas9蛋白質抵達不理想的基因突變位置，其後Cas9蛋白質會將基因斬斷成兩截；<br />\n<br />\n根據Cas9蛋白質的特性，可修改至只斬一條特定的DNA位置，其後會再提及。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）此時候，如果將盛載想修改的基因排組送到斷成兩截的基因附近，細胞便會加以利用，將原本的紫色區域改成為黃色區域。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QyefYN0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQyefYN0.jpg&h=0cd78956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但這個方法的隨機性非常之高，最終結果有可能會出現基因刪減，又或者是其他基因排組的插入。<br />\n<br />\n套用基因編輯技術於治療病人身上的話，精準度必須要非常之高，此手段明顯並不理想。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）至於新式編輯方法Prime Editing方面，同樣亦是套用CRISPR技術，但各組件及理念則有所修改。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BW8c01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBW8c01p.jpg&h=a76ac157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擁有Transcriptase Domain的Cas9變種蛋白質將會被含有預想修改基因排組的pegRNA引領到不理想的基因突變位置，而這一次只會斬斷特定的一條DNA。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖5）其後，Cas9變種蛋白質會讀取pegRNA內含的預想修改基因排組，並將一條DNA的基因排組成功修改。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bgndLs9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbgndLs9.jpg&h=bdc9299e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過一系列難以深入淺出的程序後，最終亦會完成成功修改雙方兩截的DNA。<br />\n<br />\n（圖6）紅色區域為不理想的基因修改結果(Ref2)，新式編輯方法PrimeEditing明顯優勝於舊式編輯方法HDR，但仍有一定程度的進步空間。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6qgaNGw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6qgaNGw.png&h=4dd01bee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有朝一日，CRISPR基因編輯技術定必會在治療疾病上得以普及化。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=d2c99f14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=96cdde6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-019-1711-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41586-019-1711-4&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=c3aaa52c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-019-1711-4</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-020-19136-7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41467-020-19136-7&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=b791ffa5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-020-19136-7</a>"},{"pid":"7038e25cab41309ad76508a515443d83901e708f","tid":2282362,"uid":54323,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T22:59:06.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8d173444652c04b1af8a8d5f19c0a0772d0583","tid":2282362,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7038e25cab41309ad76508a515443d83901e708f","tid":2282362,"uid":54323,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T22:59:06.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T23:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實即係好似LEGO咁將唔要的一部份拿走，砌返中意的LEGO入去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c0c146c5c880898de8b0f2b334e50fc6cc9cf9","tid":2282362,"uid":26405,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T23:16:42.000Z","msg":"睇比較新舊方法結果幅圖，即係prime editing 係改唔晒兩邊，而且有成70%係完全無效果？"},{"pid":"411c79660c27a9044c874dcf26d00500db2bbcc4","tid":2282362,"uid":275243,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e8d173444652c04b1af8a8d5f19c0a0772d0583","tid":2282362,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7038e25cab41309ad76508a515443d83901e708f","tid":2282362,"uid":54323,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T22:59:06.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T23:02:57.